Task:

Create queries for seeking contacts to persisted classes  

(JPA named queries) 

( criterias: type (contact, lead, customer), responsible sales man, country )

Queryt tyypittäin kaikkien kyseisten tyyppien etsimiseen tauluista:

@Entity
@NamedQueries({
  @NamedQuery(name = "Contact.findAll", query = "SELECT c FROM Contact c"),
  @NamedQuery(name = "Lead.findAll", query = "SELECT l FROM Lead l"),
  @NamedQuery(name = "Customer.findAll", query = "SELECT c FROM Customer c"),
  @NamedQuery(name = "Country.findAll", query="SELECT c FROM Country c"), 

})

Qyeryja toisentyyppisillä ehdoilla (näistä en vielä ole varma):

@NamedQuery(name="Contact.findByLead", query="SELECT c FROM Contact c WHERE c.lead = :lead")
@NamedQuery(name="Contact.findByCustomer", query="SELECT c FROM Contact c WHERE c.customer = :customer")

